data.description: A Cardinal Built 1330 sf beauty with 3 Br 2 Bath .  Custom Tile at the Entry, Kitchen, & Dining Room. The Vaulted Ceilings in the Living Room and Dining Room opens the visual feeling of the two rooms.    The Dining Room and the Huge Master Bedroom have Oversized Bay Windows... and the Master Bedroom has a large Dressing area and two separate Closets. The secondary Bedrooms are both Large, and both with separate Closets and New Vertical Blinds.   Doors have been replaced with 6 Panel doors.     A Large Covered Patio for the Family.   A Dimensional Roof with Ridge Caps (Coordinated with the House).   An Insulated Steel Garage Door with Opener.    This Home is very Functional for you, or your Family so see it now.   From the front Porch you can see Lights in the Hills.   The Proposed Bullet Train to Vegas and Metro Station is about 5 to 10 Minutes from this Home.
